{"tid":857900,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"長命萬歲，萬病纏身。永生不死，永遠不健康。","createTime":"2018-10-11T11:50:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T12:04:26.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"161996a7506fd21d2b6098265bca0a51cb818c83","tid":857900,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:50:10.000Z","msg":"最近興句咒人白話：祝你長命百歲，百病纏身。<br />\n<br />\n我再加<br />\n祝你長命百歲，百病纏身。年年賺大錢，全部給醫生。<br />\n<br />\n如果將整體人類當成一個巨人，而每個人則為整體人類的細胞。<br />\n<br />\n咁人類（甚至地球上大部分物種）算唔算係<br />\n長命萬歲，萬病纏身。<br />\n永生不死，永遠不健康。<br />\n<br />\n人類可不繼繁殖永續下去，但社會卻不斷的有大量戰爭、暴力、衝突、貧富懸殊、飢餓、疾病、痛苦、地震海嘯。永遠在長存及不健康的狀態。"},{"pid":"077f607ce1b222282f9c5dbe4c3f89a969901109","tid":857900,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:52:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd0f2523fe1858dcdb604899bfa07231e2ad5586","tid":857900,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:53:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ae258b08e213ac04820681e29170f728223a7b","tid":857900,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:55:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38c73600f1496954430c0971e5d46270a286d22e","tid":857900,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T12:00:32.000Z","msg":"人類是：永生不死，永不健康的物種"},{"pid":"ecb67153887e517df1426de078c11f68836da21d","tid":857900,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38c73600f1496954430c0971e5d46270a286d22e","tid":857900,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T12:00:32.000Z","msg":"人類是：永生不死，永不健康的物種"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T12:04:26.000Z","msg":"如果體內細胞，不停打杖和衝突（其實好常見）<br />\n咁呢個人一定不健康，生病中<br />\n<br />\n將人類整體物種當成一個超級巨人的話，個體為細胞<br />\n人類絕對係：<br />\n永生不死，永不健康。"}]}